{"article_id":"0ZijEi74HVzd9c4r","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"When President Trump sat down with Lester Holt yesterday ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"he essentially altered the version of James Comey ' s firing","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"that his top aides have been pressing in public .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"\" I was going to fire","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"regardless of recommendation , \"","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"he told the NBC anchor .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"The recommendation in question was a two-page memo from Deputy Attorney General Rod Rosenstein ,","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"who had been on the job for two weeks .","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"Rosenstein is \" highly respected , \"","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Trump said ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"\" he made a recommendation ,","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"but regardless of recommendation I was going to fire Comey \"","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"( who he called a \" showboat \" and a \" grandstander \" ) .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"At Wednesday ' s press briefing , Sarah Huckabee Sanders was asked :","depth":5},{"id":14,"text":"\" So it 's the White House ' s assertion","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"that Rod Rosenstein decided on his own ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"after being confirmed ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"to review Comey ' s performance ? \"","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"\" Absolutely , \"","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"she replied .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"\" And I think","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"most of America had decided on their own","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that Director Comey was not the person","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that should be leading the FBI . \"","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"But","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"if the president asked for a review","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"to buttress a move","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"he planned to take anyway ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"then Rosenstein ' s letter isn ' t the crucial document","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that was being advertised .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"Sanders told ABC ' s Jon Karl yesterday","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"she hadn ' t had the chance","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"to ask the president that question","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"about whether he had already made up his mind .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"\" Nobody was in the dark...","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"You ' re trying to create this false narrative , \"","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"she said .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"None of this affects the core question","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"of whether the president acted properly","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"in canning his FBI director .","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"But it does underscore","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"that the administration ' s rollout of this controversial decision has been shaky .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"The media narrative has moved on to whether the White House is engaging in some kind of coverup ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"with newspaper accounts challenging some of the administration ' s key points .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Chief among them :","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Trump ' s contention","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"that Comey told him three times","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"that he wasn ' t under investigation in the Russia probe .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"The Wall Street Journal quoted a Comey associate yesterday","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"as saying","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"that was \" almost farcical .","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"\"","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"If true ,","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"would that have been improper on Comey ' s part ?","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"\" I don ' t see that as a conflict of interest , \"","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Sanders said yesterday .","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"The Washington Post reported","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"that Rosenstein had threatened to resign","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"after being portrayed as the catalyst for Comey ' s dismissal .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"NBC followed up","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"by quoting two unnamed Justice Department officials","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"as saying","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"that wasn ' t true .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"The New York Times reported","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"that \" in private ,","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"aides said ,","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Mr. Trump has been nursing a collection of festering grievances ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"including Mr. Comey ' s handling of the Russia investigation , his seeming lack of interest","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"in pursuing anti-Trump leaks and the perceived disloyalty over the wiretapping claim . \"","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"That would undermine the White House contention","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that Trump ' s decision was mainly about Comey ' s handling of the Hillary Clinton email investigation and not the Russia probe .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Some of this gets down in the weeds .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"But it ' s being fueled by the apparent conflicts between the White House explanations and the press accounts .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"And Holt elicited key information with his solid questions .","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"Sarah Sanders told reporters","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"that unlike the public , they are \" obsessed with this story. \"","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"Maybe so .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"But a president firing an FBI director under these circumstances is an earthquake","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"that will have aftershocks for some weeks","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"to come .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":159,"left":92,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":92,"left":85,"right":91,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":82,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":0,"right":81,"relation":"context","nu